products.title: Genesis Black Perfect Fit Roller Blind
products.description: Their genesis range comes in 6 colour variations and is the perfect choice for a modern look. This crisp perfect fit black roller blind will look great in any room in your home and will add a touch of style. The perfect fit aspect of this blind means it can clip straight on to pvc window frames - saving space and meaning no drills or screws. Product id: sdb-pfr0171 fabric colour: black material: 100% polyester headrail: drill-free slimline frame with sleek roller casing control type: cordless spring operated energy saving rating: er2 - medium energy saving value - effective thermal retention light filtering: yes genesis black perfect fit roller blind in black.
